description:
&lt;p&gt;Following a period of restructure, we are looking to appoint to two new positions to provide operational leadership to our Facilities Teams across Dorset.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These positions will have geographical responsibilities across the county for the delivery of the full range of Facilities deliverables:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position 1 - Dorchester, Bridport, Weymouth, Portland, Sherborne&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position 2 – Wimborne, Blandford, St. Leonards, Shaftesbury&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(Candidates will therefore need to hold a clean and valid driving licence)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates will need to be enthusiastic, highly motivated and able to demonstrate the ability to support and drive change across our services, as well as providing support to the teams within their areas of responsibility.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates will need to demonstrate the ability to work autonomously and across the full Facilities and Estates services, working with other peers to deliver standardisation, best practise, lateral thinking and identification of opportunities for enhancement of quality improvements to deliver a patient centric service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working with locality managers, service managers and professionals. The successful candidate with have budget, HR, IT and Health &amp; Safety experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you enjoy a challenge and have previous experience of line management, inspiring and leading others we would like to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(Applicants will need to confirm which post they are applying for within their application)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full post of 37.5 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Employment in this post requires a Standard Disclosure and Barring Service (DBS) check. The DBS levies a charge of £23 and the Trust will recover this cost in instalments from your first 3 salary payments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants who subscribe to the DBS update service and are able to present a valid DBS certificate will not incur a charge.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name:  Rick Northwood&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title:  Facilities Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address:  richard.northwood@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
